    <h1>QuillBot Review 2026: Best Paraphrasing Tool, Zero SEO Value</h1>
    <p class="description">QuillBot is the best paraphraser on the market — 9 rewriting modes, a clean editor, and a Chrome extension that just works. It is also <strong>not a content workflow, not an SEO tool, and a clear risk if used to spin competitor articles</strong>. Here is the honest 2026 verdict on where QuillBot fits — and where it absolutely does not.</p>
