        <p class="lede-p"><strong>QuillBot is the best paraphraser on the market. It is also the worst possible foundation for SEO content.</strong> After 30 days of testing every mode on real student papers, marketing drafts, and competitor articles — plus a hard look at how Google's helpful content updates handle paraphrased text — here is the honest 2026 verdict, the situations where QuillBot is brilliant, and the one common use case where it is a trap.</p>

