            <a href="/demo/" class="cta-btn-inline">Get my free audit <span>→</span></a>
            <span class="cta-meta">24-hour delivery · No card</span>
          </div>
        </div>

        <h2 id="vs-stacc">theStacc vs QuillBot — different products, same content question</h2>
        <p>We are not in the same category. But operators considering QuillBot for content creation often end up at theStacc. Read the comparison first so you can decide which problem you are actually trying to solve.</p>

        <div class="table-wrap">
          <table>
            <thead>
              <tr><th>Feature</th><th>QuillBot</th><th>theStacc</th></tr>
            </thead>
            <tbody>
              <tr><td>Starting price</td><td>$4.17/mo annual</td><td>$99/mo</td></tr>
