              <tr><td><strong>Teams</strong></td><td>~$15/user</td><td>~$11/user</td><td>~$8/user</td><td>Premium + central billing</td></tr>
            </tbody>
          </table>
        </div>

        <p>The annual price ($4.17/mo) is roughly <strong>79% off</strong> the monthly rate — the steepest annual discount in the writing-tool category. For students and ESL writers this is among the easiest "yes" purchases in software.</p>

        <h3>The real cost if you try to build SEO content with it</h3>
        <p>QuillBot's sticker is cheap. The real cost shows up when teams misuse it for blog content and either rank for nothing or accumulate a Google penalty.</p>

